.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, folk, reggae, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, tennis, cricket, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
4. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the fan of rock and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | reggae           | rock | techno  |
| Sport         | golf | weightlifting | tennis   | cricket |

