.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, disco, folk, salsa
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, airplane, van, subway
1. the fan of disco is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the fan of pop is between the person driving the ship and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | disco | pop | folk      |
| Transport     | van | ship    | airplane  | subway |

