.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, surfing, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, airplane, ship, jet-ski
1. the person driving the train is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the ship##2
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | ice-hockey | baseball | surfing     | water-polo   |
| Transport   | ship   | airplane     | jet-ski | train |

