.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, accountant, teacher, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, bus, motorbike
1. the teacher is between the person driving the helicopter and the photographer##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the photographer is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | accountant | teacher | photographer | security-guard |
| Transport   | helicopter         | motorbike       | airplane    | bus         |

