.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, spinach, pineapple, lime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, biathlon, rowing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person eating spinach and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | lime   | pineapple      | spinach   | carrot  |
| Sport   | rowing | skiing | biathlon | rugby |

