.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, raspberry, kiwi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, satire, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato     | pumpkin | kiwi   | raspberry        |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | satire   | adventure | sports |

