.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, reading, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, indie, ambient
1. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of funk is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of classical##1
5. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the fan of classical is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | reading | board-games | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | indie          | classical     | ambient  | funk     |

