4. the manager is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | manager | software-developer | architect | paramedic     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | satire    | crime   | time-travel |

