The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the thai is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the brazilian is between the person driving the snowmobile and the nigerian##2
4. the thai is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | german | nigerian | brazilian | thai |
| Transport     | roller     | skateboard   | jet-ski | snowmobile  |

