1. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the turkish is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the ferret and the nigerian##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian | colombian | argentine |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | chinchilla  | turtle | ferret      |

