.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, video-games, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, frog, ferret
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the pony and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | video-games    | filmmaking     | drawing | traveling |
| Pet     | turtle | ferret | frog       | pony     |

 